snippet.title: YARG Setlist: Wave 6 Trailer
snippet.description:
Wave 6 is here! Check out 6 new songs featuring Good Kid, FoundiT, Creo, The Sterns, Alohaii ft. Shiki Miyoshino, and Heartsick ft. Sapphire Noel available now through the launcher! Just download/update the setlist and the songs will automatically be included in your library when you launch YARG.

Download the YARG Launcher here: https://github.com/YARC-Official/YARC-Launcher/releases

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
If you're a developer, artist, or band and are interested in contributing to YARG, feel free to join us on Discord, GitHub, or contact us via our email. We are 100% open source and always welcome anyone who wants to contribute!

Website: https://yarg.in/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/yarg
GitHub: https://github.com/YARC-Official/YARG
